  "title": "Design Engineer (Audio Visual System) - North",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></em></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Handled product design, customization, and structural modifications for simulation systems.</li>\n  <li>Engaged in on-site installation and commissioning activities.</li>\n  <li>Supported overseas projects and implementation work as required.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em><strong>Requirements:</strong></em></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Electrical/ Electronic/ Mechanical/ Mechatronics Engineering.</li>\n  <li>1–2 years of hands-on project or installation experience.</li>\n  <li>Proficient in reading technical drawings and using AutoCAD 3D.</li>\n  <li>Competent in Microsoft Office Suite.</li>\n  <li>Strong team player with good interpersonal skills.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd | 20C0270</p>\n<p>Tew Jie Wei | R22106822</p>",
